### Advent Calendar - Get Feature Status
GET {{baseUrl}}/advent-calendar/feature-status
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Advent Calendar - Set Feature Status (Admin/Super Admin only)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/advent-calendar/feature-status
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isFeatureActive": true
}

### Advent Calendar - Set Feature Status to False (Admin/Super Admin only)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/advent-calendar/feature-status
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "isFeatureActive": false
}

### Advent Calendar - Get All Entries
GET {{baseUrl}}/advent-calendar
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Advent Calendar - Get Entry by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/advent-calendar/entry123
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}

### Advent Calendar - Create Entry (Admin/Super Admin only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/advent-calendar
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "number": 1,
  "canParticipate": true,
  "isActive": true,
  "date": "2024-12-01",
  "isSpecial": false,
  "description": "Erster Tag des Adventskalenders",
  "linkUrl": "https://example.com/day1"
}

### Advent Calendar - Create Special Entry (Admin/Super Admin only)
POST {{baseUrl}}/advent-calendar
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "number": 24,
  "canParticipate": true,
  "isActive": true,
  "date": "2024-12-24",
  "isSpecial": true,
  "description": "Heiliger Abend - Spezieller Tag!",
  "linkUrl": "https://example.com/day24"
}

